CITY PAGE BACKLINK:
${formData.backlinkInterest ? "Yes, I plan to add the VetList badge / city-page backlink on our website." : "No backlink commitment yet."}
${formData.backlinkInterest ? `Preferred city page: https://vetlist.org${resolveCityPageHref() || ""}` : ""}

Please update my profile with this information. I confirm that I am authorized to make changes to this veterinary practice profile.

Thank you,
[Your Name]
[Your Title]
${formData.practiceName}`;

